---
title: One-Pot Tortelloni with Parmesan Breadcrumbs and Kale
description: Pasta + pesto + Parmesan cheese: it’s an equation that never fails. Add in a crispy panko breadcrumb topping, and now things are really starting to add up. But to really make this dish worth more than the sum of its parts, you gotta add a powerhouse veggie like kale. It takes this tortelloni bake from creamy and crusty to hale and hearty and incredibly satisfying.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pot-tortelloni-5b6134fe.jpg
